              <h2>WILDFIRE</h2>
              <p>The 2012 Dhaka fire broke out on 24 November 2012, in the Tazreen Fashion factory in the Ashulia district on the outskirts of Dhaka, Bangladesh. At least 117 people were confirmed dead in the fire, and over 200 were injured, making it the deadliest factory fire in the nation's history. </p>
              <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href=" https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&rct=j&q=&esrc=s&source=web&cd=1&cad=rja&uact=8&ved=0ahUKEwijxOKopqLYAhUCNo8KHd3KAYkQFggnMAA&url=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2012_Dhaka_fire&usg=AOvVaw37SXDdm-ZrT_CoLF1TU_3q" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
